Today is #WorldBrainDay! There is a lot you can do for a healthy brain 🧠. Here are some tips:

🏃‍♂️ Keep physically active
🍌 Eat a healthy diet
😴 Get enough sleep
🧩 Stimulate your mind
💟 Look after your heart
⛑️ Wear a helmet

The focus of this year’s World Brain Day is multiple sclerosis. Multiple sclerosis is a condition that can affect the brain and spinal cord, causing a wide range of potential symptoms, including problems with vision, arm or leg movement, sensation or balance.

Swipe 👉 to learn more!
